headline: Energy Drink Maker Celsius Gets An Earnings Jolt
summary: Celsius Holdings rallied to a nearly four-month high after sales and earnings beat analysts' expectations.  Analysts' consensus earnings estimate was for 19 cents a share on sales of $638.9 million.  Celsius acquired Alani Nu last April and Rockstar Energy's U.S. and Canada operations from PepsiCo in August.
